{"tid":1078136,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國最高檢副檢察長：行賄幾萬元　無謀取重大利益　這類人不要抓","createTime":"2019-03-26T05:48:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-27T03:51:01.000Z","uid":141151,"like":33,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"279bffe92e958baa768ac4c59dae2b6c42c00798","tid":1078136,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T05:48:51.000Z","msg":"中國最高檢副檢察長：行賄幾萬元 無謀取重大利益 這類人不要抓<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/china/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E6%9C%80%E9%AB%98%E6%AA%A2%E5%89%AF%E6%AA%A2%E5%AF%9F%E9%95%B7-%E8%A1%8C%E8%B3%84%E5%B9%BE%E8%90%AC%E5%85%83-%E7%84%A1%E8%AC%80%E5%8F%96%E9%87%8D%E5%A4%A7%E5%88%A9%E7%9B%8A-%E9%80%99%E9%A1%9E%E4%BA%BA%E4%B8%8D%E8%A6%81%E6%8A%93/?fbclid=IwAR0MNbKcKAcjPDYJPXztScJNtfct4y5hZl22xeqZgXKTA_6c-d66aACsuVw#.XJME2_gV9-g.facebook\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fchina%2F%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E6%259C%2580%25E9%25AB%2598%25E6%25AA%25A2%25E5%2589%25AF%25E6%25AA%25A2%25E5%25AF%259F%25E9%2595%25B7-%25E8%25A1%258C%25E8%25B3%2584%25E5%25B9%25BE%25E8%2590%25AC%25E5%2585%2583-%25E7%2584%25A1%25E8%25AC%2580%25E5%258F%2596%25E9%2587%258D%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%2588%25A9%25E7%259B%258A-%25E9%2580%2599%25E9%25A1%259E%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E4%25B8%258D%25E8%25A6%2581%25E6%258A%2593%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR0MNbKcKAcjPDYJPXztScJNtfct4y5hZl22xeqZgXKTA_6c-d66aACsuVw%23.XJME2_gV9-g.facebook&d=l9j%2BX5M8xayYNSKzl1ZQhqmkGRIJ7ARjMQoHd6uTSg0%3D&h=0c3908ac\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fchina%2F%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E6%259C%2580%25E9%25AB%2598%25E6%25AA%25A2%25E5%2589%25AF%25E6%25AA%25A2%25E5%25AF%259F%25E9%2595%25B7-%25E8%25A1%258C%25E8%25B3%2584%25E5%25B9%25BE%25E8%2590%25AC%25E5%2585%2583-%25E7%2584%25A1%25E8%25AC%2580%25E5%258F%2596%25E9%2587%258D%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%2588%25A9%25E7%259B%258A-%25E9%2580%2599%25E9%25A1%259E%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E4%25B8%258D%25E8%25A6%2581%25E6%258A%2593%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR0MNbKcKAcjPDYJPXztScJNtfct4y5hZl22xeqZgXKTA_6c-d66aACsuVw%23.XJME2_gV9-g.facebook&h=ce0e9836\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/china/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E6%9C%80%E9%AB%98%E6%AA%A2%E5%89%AF%E6%AA%A2%E5%AF%9F%E9%95%B7-%E8%A1%8C%E8%B3%84%E5%B9%BE%E8%90%AC%E5%85%83-%E7%84%A1%E8%AC%80%E5%8F%96%E9%87%8D%E5%A4%A7%E5%88%A9%E7%9B%8A-%E9%80%99%E9%A1%9E%E4%BA%BA%E4%B8%8D%E8%A6%81%E6%8A%93/?fbclid=IwAR0MNbKcKAcjPDYJPXztScJNtfct4y5hZl22xeqZgXKTA_6c-d66aACsuVw#.XJME2_gV9-g.facebook</a><br />\n<br />\n內地正舉行兩會（人大會議和政協會議），全國政協委員、最高檢察院副檢察長孫謙，在政協小組會議上稱，過去私營經濟的個別老闆，一發現涉嫌犯罪就送進派出所，從司法角度來看，「不應該動不動就抓人、封企業，一封企業就癱瘓」。孫謙又說，「有些行賄犯罪，只要沒有謀取重大的違法利益，就給了幾萬塊錢，這一類不要抓人」。<br />\n<br />\n孫謙在全國政協十三屆二次會議社科界別小組討論上，就保護民營經濟發言。他稱，關於辦理涉及民營經濟的案件如何準確適用法律，最高檢察院出台了好幾份文件，核心就是「不要輕易抓人」。<br />\n<br />\n他續說， 「有些行賄犯罪，只要沒有謀取重大的違法利益，就給了幾萬塊錢，這一類不要抓人。過去一涉嫌犯罪就給送進派出所，結果造成整個企業癱瘓。」<br />\n<br />\n孫謙提到，他曾去某省調查研究，過程中發現全省排名前一百的私營經濟企業老闆，有幾十個被抓，造成工人下崗、企業停工停產，政府稅收也受影響，「這個不得了。你們都知道民營經濟在中國改革開放四十年來的貢獻，在國家經濟中的分量。」孫謙認為，如何依法保護民營企業，也應該是政協委員參政議政的一項重要議題。<br />\n<br />\n根據最高檢察院網站，孫謙畢業於吉林大學法律系，有法學博士學位，亦是該校教授、博士生導師，1982年加入中國共產黨，現為最高檢察院黨組成員、副檢察長。<br />\n<br />\n相關報道：財新 / 新京報"},{"pid":"49088f5bacc553a877fe5251ed9359c2151b2437","tid":1078136,"uid":156363,"like":30,"dislike":0,"score":30,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T05:53:14.000Z","msg":"貪曾咪白坐冤枉監？"},{"pid":"bedc7c948579697406fc5de55663801c2e8d67d1","tid":1078136,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T05:54:59.000Z","msg":"何志平？"},{"pid":"e3fa1003c7221a9888b59fb14cc6cab9f0040e8d","tid":1078136,"uid":52946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T06:52:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39a802b4f7d59a136fa6751c8aa8bce3208c04e5","tid":1078136,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T07:20:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2272db77ed66e9e59125d6939bbd1f43e219b64a","tid":10